    "body": "Thanks for your reply,\r\n\r\nI just found a solution (see above) but I suppose your is better.\r\n\r\n```\r\nvar search = instantsearch({\r\n    appId: APPID,\r\n    apiKey: APPKEY,\r\n    indexName: 'products',\r\n    urlSync: true,\r\n    searchFunction: function(helper){\r\n        if (helper.state.disjunctiveFacetsRefinements.cat_color) {\r\n            search.helper.state.distinct = false;\r\n        } else {\r\n            search.helper.state.distinct = true;\r\n        }\r\n        helper.search();\r\n    }\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\nThanks again.\r\n\r\n",
